All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.rap.rwt.lifecycle.IEntryPointFactory
class EntryPointFactory

Simple implementation of an org.eclipse.rap.rwt.lifecycle.IEntryPointFactory. A concrete org.eclipse.rap.rwt.lifecycle.IEntryPoint implementing object can be set, which is then returned by the create() method.

This factory implementation is used to be passed to the entry point configuration in the ApplicationConfigurationBean.

Benjamin Wolff
